      "instruction": "<p>Combine <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and your <strong>curry powder</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/1 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> chopped chicken pieces </strong>and mix well until they're completely coated – this is your <strong>coated chicken</strong></p>",
