    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cover a baking tray (or two!) with<strong> tin foil</strong> (to avoid mess!)</p><p>Add the <strong>coated chicken</strong> to the baking tray[s] and put it under the grill for 10-12 min or until the chicken is cooked through and starting to char (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>tandoori chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1686068515759-x200.jpg",
