        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways</p><p>Scrape out the <strong>inner</strong> <strong>seeds</strong> with a teaspoon and set aside for later, then dice the rest</p><p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Dice the <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1686068520899-x200.jpg",
