            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> cucumber seeds </strong>and the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>natural</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong> in a bowl with the <strong>mint sauce</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>mint raita</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>tandoori chicken</strong> over the <strong>nigella</strong> <strong>rice</strong> with the <strong>kachumber salad</strong> and <strong>mint raita</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
